room_title: Escape room "Under Pressure" by Escapology Huntsville in Huntsville
room_address: 930 Old Monrovia Rd NW, Suite A, Huntsville AL 35806
room_description: The year is 1944: the height of World War II. Onboard the Steel Shark, deep in the North Atlantic Ocean, your team is on a mission to spy on the German Battle Cruiser, Scheer. Suddenly, sabotaged by German agents, the submarine goes into emergency mode and only 60 minutes of reserve oxygen remains! You and the crew must act quickly so you can stay alive and continue your mission!
